{"tid":152741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史有如果]如果當年港英政府冇實行高薪養廉政策","createTime":"2017-03-12T04:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T14:19:08.000Z","uid":90577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af2670180d69b88e281b5a329631bb319985be5f","tid":152741,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"今時今日點解高登同連登咁撚多考警or考公務員post,全因為黑警,甚至所有公務員都有一個共通點,薪高糧準<br />\n而公務員之所以成為人人爭住要既鐵飯碗,主因都係因為70年代開始實行既高薪養廉政策,令公務員人工同福利大大增加,吸引大把人狗衝去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我有時諗,如果當年港英冇實行高薪養廉政策,今時今日公務員既薪酬同一般勞動市場差唔多,唔知今日仲會唔會有大把身體好誠實既人去考黑警?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登D考黑警同考政府走狗既post會唔會冇晒咁劑??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be3340a4c8cb3a7a729c13754c9cbe930628b6a","tid":152741,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇既話應該收足咁多年片"},{"pid":"7f8d8666bb384400d2f52e2363550146cbac6f26","tid":152741,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇既話應該收足咁多年片</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n689 人工夠高過晒歐美啲總統啦，咪又係會發生ugl<br />\n<br />\n人既貪念根本無窮無盡，單純高薪唔會養到廉"},{"pid":"d56b828fbcf76946b224bf3aa69e17704d14e084","tid":152741,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"咁當年係高薪養廉<br />\n<br />\n97後係高薪養垃圾和貪官"},{"pid":"ab1427480538e4d6d70571fc69f28f1f29033e12","tid":152741,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:18:49.000Z","msg":